OL,3,CClub legends promise to stay in touch
OL,4,Cafter mass gathering of ex-players
OL,6,FGranada Reports sports correspondent
OL,7,FMike Hall was invited along to the ex-
OL,8,Fplayers' reunion.
OL,10,FMore than 60 ex-Manchester City
OL,11,Fplayers have gathered for their
OL,12,Fbiggest-ever reunion.
OL,14,FThey met for a special celebration in
OL,15,FManchester's El Rincon tapas
OL,16,Frestaurant - among them club legends
OL,17,Flike Mike Summerbee, Joe Corrigan and
OL,18,FDenis Tueart.
