OL,3,CClub legends promise to stay in touch
OL,4,Cafter mass gathering of ex-players
OL,6,FMany of the City greats made a bee-
OL,7,Fline for Watson, to hug him, shake his
OL,8,Fhand and show him how much he is
OL,9,Ftreasured.
OL,11,FThe event marked a reboot of City's
OL,12,FFormer Players' Association and was a
OL,13,Fchance to catch up and to reminisce.
OL,15,FAll those who attended were all given
OL,16,Fa "legacy number" - calculated by ex-
OL,17,FCity and England midfielder David
OL,18,FWhite, who with the help of former
OL,19,Fteammate Ian Brightwell, created a
OL,20,Fspreadsheet containing a list of names
OL,21,Fand dates of each player's debut.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
