OL,3,CClub legends promise to stay in touch
OL,4,Cafter mass gathering of ex-players
OL,6,FAll the City legends present said the
OL,7,Fparty would definitely not be the last.
OL,9,FPaul Lake, who graced City's former
OL,10,FMaine Road ground between 1983-96,
OL,11,Fsaid: "Some of them have played in
OL,12,Ffront of 90,000 fans years ago and yet
OL,13,Fthey may be living by themselves or
OL,14,Fthey may have become a carer or they
OL,15,Fmay be struggling with their own
OL,16,Fhealth.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
