OL,3,CClub legends promise to stay in touch
OL,4,Cafter mass gathering of ex-players
OL,6,F"So we can connect with them. We can
OL,7,Fprovide signposting to the support
OL,8,Fprovided by the PFA(Professional
OL,9,FFootballers' Association). We can
OL,10,Fensure all of our family of former
OL,11,FCity players are reconnected.
OL,13,F"Everyone's been made to feel special.
OL,14,FIf you've played one game for
OL,15,FManchester City or over 600, no-one
OL,16,Fgets forgotten; everyone's going to be
OL,17,Fcelebrated and everybody is going to
OL,18,Fbe made to feel important."
